## Managing Epics

**List all epics:**
```bash
s9 dashboard
```

**Show epic details:**
```bash
s9 epic show EPC-H-0001
```

**Create new epic:**
```bash
s9 epic create --title "Feature Name" --priority HIGH
```

**Update epic:**
```bash
s9 epic update EPC-H-0001 --status UNDERWAY
```


