## Relationship with Tasks

Epics serve as parent containers for related tasks:

- Each task references its parent epic (if applicable)
- Use `s9 task create --epic EPC-H-0001` to link tasks to epics
- Dashboard shows epic progress based on subtask completion
- Tasks can span multiple roles (Architect, Engineer, Tester, etc.)


